Environment: Next.js 15 App Router app at assembly.meavo.app (dev port 3001). Satellite of meavo-gateway on the shared Neon Postgres DB.

## Stack

- Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript strict, React 19, `@/*` ‚Üí `./src/*`
- Tailwind CSS 3; in-house UI kit in `src/components/ui.tsx` ‚Äî no external component library
- Prisma 6 via `@meavo/db` (schema owned by the meavo-db repo, shared Neon Postgres)
- NextAuth v5 JWT (Google SSO, invite-only) for staff; HMAC cookie sessions (`src/lib/partner-session.ts`) for partners
- `@meavo/navigation` top nav; Google Sheets API sync; Vercel Blob uploads; Vercel AI Gateway (Gemini) translations

## Do NOT

- Edit the Prisma schema here ‚Äî it lives in meavo-db; bump the `@meavo/db` git ref
- Run `prisma db push` (disabled ‚Äî shared DB, can drop other apps' tables)
- Write to Sales-owned tables (`Deal`, `QuoteLineItem`, ‚Ä¶) ‚Äî read-only for deal linking
- Send email directly ‚Äî enqueue to `NotificationOutbox` via `src/lib/notifications/enqueue.ts`
- Import `@/lib/auth` in `src/middleware.ts` (edge) ‚Äî use `@/lib/auth.config`
- Skip `requireMeavoAccess()` / `requirePartnerSession(slug)` in Server Actions
- Add a staff route segment without adding it to `MEVAO_RESERVED_SEGMENTS` (`src/lib/constants.ts`) ‚Äî `/{slug}` catch-all serves partners

## Code layout

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Staff pages (auth-gated) | `src/app/(meavo)/` ‚Äî assemblies, calendar, deals, library (partners/questionnaire/resources) |
| Partner portal (code login) | `src/app/[slug]/` ‚Äî assembly list, questionnaire wizard, resources |
| Server Actions | `src/app/actions/` ‚Äî assemblies, partner, deals, resources, questionnaire-translations, meavo |
| API routes | `src/app/api/` ‚Äî auth, cron/import, photos, resources, resource-files |
| Domain logic + integrations | `src/lib/` ‚Äî flat feature-prefixed modules (`assembly-*`, `questionnaire-*`, `sheets-*`) |
| Auth | `src/lib/auth.ts`, `auth.config.ts`, `meavo-auth.ts`, `partner-session.ts`, `src/middleware.ts` |
| Tests | N/A ‚Äî no test suite |

## Data flow

```
Google Sheet (Deliveries tab)
   ‚Üï sheets-import.ts / sheets-export.ts
Assembly rows in shared Neon Postgres  ‚Üêlink‚Üí  Deal (Sales-owned, read-only)
   ‚Üë staff Server Actions (requireMeavoAccess)
   ‚Üë partner Server Actions (requirePartnerSession) ‚Üí submissions, answers, Blob photos
   ‚Üí NotificationOutbox (gateway sends email)
Cron: GET /api/cron/import every 30 min (CRON_SECRET) re-imports the sheet
```

Every assembly mutation touching sheet-mirrored fields must write back via `appendAssemblyRow` / `updateAssemblyRow` / `clearAssemblyRow` and record `sheetRowNumber` / `sheetSyncError`.

